{"tid":1816623,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"「和你宵」人血眾籌？怕俾人利用唔該好好監察！","createTime":"2020-01-08T11:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T09:03:16.000Z","uid":75924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ba3599d23564722d5f78a06f29678399f1dd6794","tid":1816623,"uid":75924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:09:29.000Z","msg":"可以睇咗前文先：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1767283/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1767283/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【食人血饅頭】「和你宵」發起人被揭走數前科 籌近83萬 網民要求回水：<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191203/60339001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191203%2F60339001&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=5ae6fba7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191203%2F60339001&h=34290860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191203/60339001</a><br />\n<br />\n直到距離年宵仲有唔夠十日，<br />\n「和你宵」嘅Facebook Page租鋪仲喺到keep住update，<br />\n但就至今未有Confirm email，<br />\n而早前報稱嘅地址明明係裝修緊，租唔到做年宵。<br />\n希望大家認清一個事實，<br />\n即使用糖衣包裝，入面都有可能係人血饅頭，<br />\n請嗰啲俾咗錢眾籌、買飛、投檔嘅人，<br />\n好好監察呢件事，<br />\n唔好俾人覺得黃絲好易呃。<br />\n可能有人話搞手都要食飯，<br />\n所以先籌完咁多錢租場仲要收場租、收入場費，<br />\n但唔該搞手既然用「和你宵」嘅活動名義，<br />\n就要做啲對得住手足嘅事，多咗嘅錢捐出去。<br />\n<br />\np.s. 其實我真係冇乜心情行年宵，每次嘅歡愉都令我醒起死去、被捕、受傷、還押、流離失所嘅手足，覺得自己嘅快樂係建築喺佢地身上。請大家清醒，今次嘅運動開始咗，一旦完結得毫無收穫，我地將要負上更大代價，而以上嘅手足只會被白白犧牲，請用行動明志。"},{"pid":"545925c75ada980d642b01185fa7c8c141454d5e","tid":1816623,"uid":75924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PefVAjH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPefVAjH.jpg&h=7440767b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2e1bd7397e00f58a0b44f99e0b3f988ee826ee5","tid":1816623,"uid":75924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:47:05.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2a5c3b62efc40c92fd973967b4bca211ccab2832","tid":1816623,"uid":270261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:03:16.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n大家要理智<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/25982/%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%9C%88-%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%B5-%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%B5-26003/%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%B5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F25982%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E8%2589%25B2%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%259C%2588-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25AE%25B5-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2596%2593%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25AE%25B5-26003%2F%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25AE%25B5&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=bd55c0e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/25982/%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%9C%88-%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%B5-%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%B5-26003/%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%B5</a><br />\n<br />\n見呢個好似可信D"}]}